                        <interp inst="t18491126-name-477" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES CHINN</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> That was the room I went into.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
