                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, G</hi> 374). I produce a certificate of Charles Sleigh's conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—George Jones, convicted Feb.</hi> 7, 1848, <hi rend="italic">confined six month</hi>)—he is the man.</p>
